WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:04.960
Well, good morning, family, good evening wherever you are.

00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:08.480
I talk to people all over the world, so I always say morning.

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:11.080
Thank you for joining us again tonight.

00:00:11.760 --> 00:00:15.307
We have some work to do.

00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:24.339
I don't even really know where to start other than I just want to give God all the praise and glory for what he's doing.

00:00:24.339 --> 00:00:27.005
As we see, prayer changes things.

00:00:27.005 --> 00:00:41.707
We see Pam Bondi and the man saying that he wanted to harm her, trying to pay $45,000, which was around—I saw 50 on the wanted.

00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:49.590
As I have been praying over this today, I have more to share with you.

00:00:50.770 --> 00:00:55.591
The Lord is revealing more to us, Diana and I, and my children.

00:00:55.591 --> 00:01:11.687
As we were driving around, I saw a football, and Pam Bondi was holding a football, but I didn't understand what I was seeing on the 19th.

00:01:18.969 --> 00:01:28.960
When I saw her holding the football, I said, 'This looks like a football, but it has layers.

00:01:28.960 --> 00:01:39.880
' It transformed from a football to a pinwheel that had layers that looked dark black and white.

00:01:40.290 --> 00:01:44.266
That's why I said it looked like one of those Hostess cupcakes.

00:01:46.712 --> 00:01:53.428
It had the frosting all in it, and it was pinwheel-looking, and the football turned into that.

00:01:53.759 --> 00:01:58.700
The Lord said there are many layers to this for her to expose.

00:02:06.103 --> 00:02:16.260
She's going to expose this darkness, but she needs a little bit more information to nail the coffin closed and make it a closed case.

00:02:16.260 --> 00:02:24.080
She has enough evidence that she's going to run with this.

00:02:24.470 --> 00:02:32.239
The Lord said because of what she will expose, there will be a price on her head.

00:02:32.599 --> 00:02:37.497
I saw a price tag of over $50,000.

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:46.319
I saw the zeros, and I saw not 45, but 50.

00:02:46.679 --> 00:02:58.600
As I saw this red list, I saw Alex Jones was going to expose some things that were dark, and what he would say would be credible.

00:02:59.960 --> 00:03:03.140
I saw Tucker Carlson on the list.

00:03:03.140 --> 00:03:12.754
I saw many judges on this hit list and people in high authority—Giuliani.

00:03:12.754 --> 00:03:22.080
I saw many people on this list, and some of their names had more zeros than others.

00:03:22.570 --> 00:03:37.360
The Lord said, 'You must pray for their protection, for they are on a list to be taken out, and you must intercede for them, for this is bigger than you realize.

00:03:37.360 --> 00:03:55.910
' I saw foreign people—and I can't go into all that—who were funding this through crypto.

00:03:55.920 --> 00:04:07.600
That's all I'm going to say.

00:04:10.640 --> 00:04:27.189
We're going to continue to pray for them because the Lord said what was said today was communication.

00:04:27.859 --> 00:04:37.440
It's bigger than the man that was caught today; this is communication.

00:04:40.639 --> 00:04:45.520
Why would they have this gambling ring?

00:04:45.520 --> 00:04:52.080
And why would some of these people who are worth millions participate in this?

00:04:54.213 --> 00:04:56.227
They're already worth millions of dollars.

00:04:57.187 --> 00:05:03.166
Why would they risk their chance of going to prison for a couple million dollars for these big people?

00:05:15.199 --> 00:05:17.188
You are thinking too small.

00:05:17.188 --> 00:05:20.880
That's what the Lord said.

00:05:21.720 --> 00:05:22.560
Blackmail.

00:05:24.560 --> 00:05:24.960
Blackmail tapes, videotapes.

00:05:28.960 --> 00:05:38.230
The Lord said videotapes with them doing certain things with certain young people.

00:05:38.240 --> 00:05:40.240
Blackmail.

00:05:40.240 --> 00:05:46.800
'Do what we tell you to do or more will come out.

00:05:46.800 --> 00:05:53.066
' This is deeper than what you can ever understand.

00:05:53.066 --> 00:06:02.526
And the Lord said—and that's all I will say about that—but you must know that it doesn't make sense.

00:06:04.240 --> 00:06:08.800
You can play the video of what the Lord said.

00:06:08.800 --> 00:06:09.360
Yes, sir.

00:06:10.195 --> 00:06:12.699
Go ahead, son.

00:06:15.450 --> 00:06:23.441
Just play it right there and show them what the Lord said.

00:06:23.441 --> 00:06:25.789
Football, baseball...

00:06:28.180 --> 00:06:29.540
oh, and sports people.

00:06:29.540 --> 00:06:32.907
And then he talked to us about LeBron James, and I thought that was interesting.

00:06:32.907 --> 00:06:34.360
He said he'll retire soon.

00:06:34.360 --> 00:06:36.125
Everybody says, 'Well, of course he will.

00:06:36.125 --> 00:06:38.259
' No, I'm talking about something more to this.

00:06:38.800 --> 00:06:43.656
I saw the king be dethroned—the name King James.

00:06:54.800 --> 00:07:02.160
There's more to this, and it was not a good thing.

00:07:04.329 --> 00:07:07.919
The Lord said he would be dethroned.

00:07:07.919 --> 00:07:10.639
A humbling is coming.

00:07:11.840 --> 00:07:18.639
I don't know what that means, but I saw a humbling coming, a play on words.

00:07:21.787 --> 00:07:25.440
I'm just telling you what I saw.

00:07:25.440 --> 00:07:38.251
There's something more to a dethroning of a king who considers himself way above the King of Kings, the Lord of Lords, Jesus Christ.

00:07:38.251 --> 00:07:42.819
King James Version, King—all this stuff was in the air.

00:07:42.819 --> 00:07:48.590
But the Lord said, 'There's about to be something huge happen in the NBA.

00:07:48.590 --> 00:07:53.382
There's about to be something huge happen in the NFL and the major league.

00:07:53.382 --> 00:07:58.080
' He said, 'Watch what I'm about to do in these areas.

00:07:58.080 --> 00:08:00.879
' So, that's what we were praying over.

00:08:05.455 --> 00:08:12.080
You see, it's bigger than you realize.

00:08:12.080 --> 00:08:15.680
The Lord said this several weeks ago.

00:08:16.239 --> 00:08:27.749
He said, 'Pray for an exposing of dark things: NFL, Major League Baseball, and the NBA.

00:08:27.749 --> 00:08:30.840
' It will be in all these arenas.

00:08:31.290 --> 00:08:34.399
I saw major corruption.

00:08:34.399 --> 00:08:36.813
The Lord said it will be an uncovering.

00:08:36.813 --> 00:08:38.720
And that's what this pinwheel is.

00:08:38.720 --> 00:08:42.089
And I'm telling you, she had a football.

00:08:42.379 --> 00:08:43.800
I said, 'What is this?

00:08:43.800 --> 00:08:48.080
' because we're not even talking about football; we're talking about basketball and some of this stuff.

00:08:48.080 --> 00:08:51.067
But the Lord said there's deep dark corruption.

00:08:51.067 --> 00:09:38.310
And if you go back to what I saw concerning the children, consider the children trafficking.

00:09:38.320 --> 00:09:45.670
It's much deeper than most of you will ever realize.

00:09:45.680 --> 00:09:52.941
But as this happens, if we pray into this, the Lord said he has a hand on it.

00:09:53.110 --> 00:10:00.080
I'm telling you, we will see revival break out in major sporting events.

00:10:00.080 --> 00:10:15.024
I saw major key players having a major revival and the Holy Ghost taking over the NFL, NBA, and Major League Baseball.

00:10:15.472 --> 00:10:29.200
We're going to see people that are going to get really radical for Jesus in the days ahead, a major revival they will be used to bring forth.

00:10:29.200 --> 00:10:36.240
The Lord is going to pour out his spirit on our sports.

00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:42.217
People will idolize them like gods, like Michael Jordans and all the celebrities.

00:10:42.217 --> 00:10:48.079
The Lord said he's going to use that celebrity for his glory for bringing in the harvest.

00:10:48.079 --> 00:10:51.154
Watch what he does with these young people.

00:10:52.891 --> 00:11:03.200
But even more so with the music industry—the Lord said pray over the music industry.

00:11:04.040 --> 00:11:07.760
Pray over all this for there's an uncovering.

00:11:07.760 --> 00:11:22.960
Even when I told you I saw a new Democratic woman being groomed by the devil, hand-selected by the devil, I saw this woman being raised up and appointed.

00:11:25.680 --> 00:11:34.026
Even when I told you yesterday I saw this new pastor coming to Australia—I keep seeing these key figures.

00:11:34.026 --> 00:11:39.040
The Lord's hand-selecting people, and the devil's trying to hand-select people.

00:11:39.620 --> 00:11:42.869
It's interesting to me because I keep seeing both sides.

00:11:43.623 --> 00:11:52.1000
The Lord's showing me the devil picking people to try to cause great distraction and disruption in the move.

00:11:52.1000 --> 00:11:56.260
And then you see God saying, 'I'm raising up these people.

00:11:56.260 --> 00:12:03.189
I'm going to raise up new men with great voices like David's, Hannah's, and Esther's, and they're going to be prayer people.

00:12:03.189 --> 00:12:05.100
They're going to be the closers.

00:12:05.100 --> 00:12:09.860
' The Lord keeps talking about all this, but then I keep seeing the enemy and he has his plan.

00:12:09.860 --> 00:12:13.440
But we know who has the greater plan.

00:12:13.440 --> 00:12:16.746
Greater is he that is in us than he that is in the world.

00:12:17.546 --> 00:12:27.531
The Lord told us, 'You're about to see weather manipulation, weaponized weather more than what you've ever seen before.

00:12:27.531 --> 00:12:45.360
' He said that even last night with ice storms, winter cyclones, heavy snowfall, blizzard conditions in Buffalo, and lake effect snow that will be the largest we've ever seen.

00:12:45.360 --> 00:12:50.630
I'm talking about seeing major weather events in the days ahead.

00:12:50.630 --> 00:12:53.732
Well, you say, 'Well, Brandon, we have weather events all the time.

00:12:53.732 --> 00:12:59.236
' Yes, but this is going to be different from what I saw.

00:12:59.236 --> 00:13:08.920
I saw major winds, major straight-line winds, and power outages that would go for a thousand miles.

00:13:11.257 --> 00:13:14.399
I'm talking about crippling ice storms.

00:13:14.629 --> 00:13:16.754
The Lord said, 'You have to pray over the weather.

00:13:16.754 --> 00:13:18.996
' That's why I brought all that up last night.

00:13:19.307 --> 00:13:30.720
I was trying to encourage you to use your authority over drought and rain.

00:13:30.720 --> 00:13:32.808
As he is, so are we in this world.

00:13:33.560 --> 00:13:40.527
The Lord was showing us: 'Brandon, if I can call peace to the storms, I've given you the ability to pray over it also.

00:13:40.527 --> 00:13:44.399
' As he is, so are we in this world.

00:13:44.548 --> 00:13:53.120
I just wanted to encourage you all when I showed you how much rain northern Oklahoma got, all over Tulsa.

00:13:55.120 --> 00:14:12.110
Every time I call in a certain number, I say I'm waiting for over five inches of rain to come over our land, fill our rivers, our ponds, our creeks, and our lakes so that we don't have a drought.

00:14:12.110 --> 00:14:13.623
We take authority over drought.

00:14:13.623 --> 00:14:15.947
We call the rain in Jesus' name.

00:14:16.827 --> 00:14:18.834
You have authority to do that.

00:14:18.834 --> 00:14:20.434
Pray over your weather.

00:14:27.120 --> 00:14:30.655
There it is, right there.

00:14:37.972 --> 00:14:40.449
Everywhere in Tulsa, the rain came.

00:14:40.760 --> 00:14:45.760
That's what the Lord was trying to show you.

00:14:45.760 --> 00:14:47.999
You can do that to your town.

00:14:47.999 --> 00:14:49.635
You can call in the rain.

00:14:49.884 --> 00:14:58.800
That's why I was praying over Australia, because I saw a great drought and that even the kangaroos would die because there's no water.

00:14:59.080 --> 00:15:05.839
I saw the lakes and the ponds completely dry with big cracks, and the land was like tumbleweeds blowing across.

00:15:10.830 --> 00:15:11.867
It was so bad.

00:15:12.116 --> 00:15:14.440
The Lord said, 'Pray for the rain.

00:15:15.519 --> 00:15:16.399
Pray for the rain.

00:15:16.399 --> 00:15:18.390
' That's what I was trying to show you.

00:15:19.057 --> 00:15:23.590
We started calling it in because we hadn't had rain in September, October, or November.

00:15:26.640 --> 00:15:29.750
Hey sweetie, you want to come sit by me?

00:15:30.399 --> 00:15:33.013
I'll get out and then you can come sit down.

00:15:33.013 --> 00:15:35.680
I have my buddy.

00:15:35.680 --> 00:15:37.009
Sorry, I didn't want to disturb you.

00:15:37.519 --> 00:15:38.639
You're good.

00:15:38.639 --> 00:15:45.110
Come sit down by me.

00:15:47.120 --> 00:15:53.110
You look so marvelous.

00:15:53.760 --> 00:15:56.456
So, we're just talking about all the rain and everything.

00:15:56.456 --> 00:16:01.600
We were praying over the rain, believing God for supernatural rain.

00:16:01.600 --> 00:16:05.666
If you ever read anything, you hold it out of your mouth, don't you?

00:16:06.079 --> 00:16:08.109
Well, you can read about the blood.

00:16:08.109 --> 00:16:08.969
I have the book.

00:16:08.969 --> 00:16:10.130
We read that book last night.

00:16:10.760 --> 00:16:13.635
When you started reading, I felt the presence of the Lord.

00:16:13.635 --> 00:16:14.311
Did you?

00:16:14.311 --> 00:16:16.700
I don't know if they did, but I did.

00:16:18.027 --> 00:16:19.236
That's all that matters.

00:16:20.480 --> 00:16:23.508
But I'm reading about the precious blood of Jesus.

00:16:23.508 --> 00:16:27.440
You know, these little pocketbooks you can get for a buck.

00:16:28.533 --> 00:16:36.149
I love reading stuff like that, filling yourself up and being controlled by the Holy Ghost.

00:16:36.434 --> 00:16:43.787
We were listening to Corrie ten Boom today, and it was wonderful.

00:16:50.491 --> 00:16:50.959
It was on YouTube and it blessed me.

00:16:53.199 --> 00:17:00.399
It made me really go deep inside of myself to say, 'Listen, you've got to come up higher.

00:17:00.399 --> 00:17:01.720
' Beautiful.

00:17:13.879 --> 00:17:15.739
She challenged me, this lady did.

00:17:15.739 --> 00:17:21.371
We didn't even finish it, but I just want to encourage everyone to find things that will inspire you.

00:17:21.623 --> 00:17:29.497
Find things that will fan your flame to keep that fire going.

00:17:29.497 --> 00:17:35.960
Don't wait on your pastor or whoever is over you that you listen to.

00:17:36.880 --> 00:17:41.420
Don't wait on them to feed you Wednesdays and Sundays or whenever you go to church.

00:17:41.420 --> 00:17:47.720
You've got to have that bulldog-on-a-bone faith to say, 'Hey, I'm going to feed myself.

00:17:47.720 --> 00:17:50.260
I've got to get out there and get a hold of something.

00:17:50.260 --> 00:17:54.224
I cannot wait for somebody to spoon-feed me.

00:17:54.224 --> 00:17:57.840
I've got to have enough to be a scavenger.

00:17:57.840 --> 00:18:05.302
I'm going to find something and live by faith, and I don't need somebody else to feed me.

00:18:05.302 --> 00:18:06.559
I'm going to feed myself.

00:18:06.559 --> 00:18:08.080
' That's what Diana and I have always done.

00:18:08.765 --> 00:18:15.200
When Megan was first diagnosed with autism, we couldn't really go to church because it was such a distraction.

00:18:19.154 --> 00:18:21.933
For all those years, we just learned how to feed ourselves.

00:18:21.933 --> 00:18:22.550
We fought.

00:18:24.110 --> 00:18:32.160
I said we're going to keep going with this and we're going to find the word for whatever we need.

00:18:33.360 --> 00:18:35.200
A lot of times, it was always Kenneth E.

00:18:35.200 --> 00:18:35.920
Hagin.

00:18:36.280 --> 00:18:45.040
I listen to Brother Hagin most of all, and then to the people we listen to now.

00:18:45.760 --> 00:18:48.720
Just keep fanning that flame.

00:18:48.720 --> 00:18:50.200
Listen to Lynn Hammond.

00:18:50.200 --> 00:18:52.959
Stir up how to pray in the spirit.

00:18:52.959 --> 00:18:56.480
How bad do you want change in your life?

00:18:56.480 --> 00:19:01.669
How hungry and desperate are you for change?

00:19:02.738 --> 00:19:07.531
Are you willing to go out and look for something versus sitting there waiting?

00:19:07.942 --> 00:19:12.979
I'm telling you, it comes to the point where I see a lot of these people say, 'Brandon, I need all this.

00:19:12.979 --> 00:19:15.119
' Get it.

00:19:15.119 --> 00:19:16.560
Be a contender.

00:19:16.560 --> 00:19:17.760
Fight for it.

00:19:17.760 --> 00:19:19.810
Nobody's going to just give it to you.

00:19:19.810 --> 00:19:22.400
You have to want it bad enough.

00:19:22.400 --> 00:19:23.147
I want change.

00:19:23.147 --> 00:19:25.066
I want the Holy Ghost in my life.

00:19:25.066 --> 00:19:26.959
I want the glory and the presence.

00:19:26.959 --> 00:19:42.293
I want Jesus manifested in my home so that whenever I have an issue, when you're overcoming something, when you get a bad report, or when you have a bill you can't pay and the creditors are calling, you know what to do.

00:19:46.444 --> 00:19:48.360
If you have a need, you sow a seed.

00:19:48.360 --> 00:19:49.760
That's what we learned.

00:19:52.489 --> 00:19:55.710
He said he gives you wisdom to get wealth.

00:19:55.710 --> 00:19:59.880
So, we believe God and he gives us wisdom to make money.

00:19:59.880 --> 00:20:02.240
But what happens if you need a doctor's report?

00:20:02.820 --> 00:20:04.879
You find scripture.

00:20:04.879 --> 00:20:06.479
That's what we always do.

00:20:06.479 --> 00:20:07.866
We go back to the word.

00:20:09.314 --> 00:20:16.080
Find scriptures that pertain to what you're believing for and quote those scriptures over your life.

00:20:16.857 --> 00:20:18.411
We have Bibles everywhere.

00:20:18.411 --> 00:20:22.320
Diana got a waterproof Bible.

00:20:22.720 --> 00:20:24.300
I thought that was perfect for the end times.

00:20:24.300 --> 00:20:25.840
You could hide it in the woods.

00:20:44.729 --> 00:20:45.093
The Antichrist is going to take everybody's Bible away.

00:20:46.916 --> 00:20:48.270
I don't even think that would burn.

00:20:53.670 --> 00:20:55.164
I just know we're in a time like we've never seen before, and it's going to keep increasing.

00:20:55.164 --> 00:21:00.799
As of the 23rd, I know there is an acceleration, and we're about to see things we've never seen before.

00:21:00.799 --> 00:21:09.546
I have an urgency to come on here all the time to pray and to tell you all that Jesus Christ is coming and you've got to get your house in order.

00:21:09.546 --> 00:21:11.729
People ask, 'What does that mean, Brandon?

00:21:11.729 --> 00:21:20.470
' Well, what does that feel like to you?

00:21:20.480 --> 00:21:23.146
What is the Lord telling you to do?

00:21:37.679 --> 00:21:37.959
Do you have an urgency in your spirit to draw close to him?

00:21:37.959 --> 00:21:38.239
Does he know you?

00:21:45.300 --> 00:21:45.590
If you were to have a face-to-face encounter with the Lord, would he say, 'I know them'?

00:21:50.320 --> 00:21:54.846
Or would he say, "You know, you may know a lot about the Father, but does he know you?

00:21:54.846 --> 00:22:04.114
Do you just go and visit once a month or once a year at church, or do you have a relationship every single day with him?

00:22:04.114 --> 00:22:12.519
" If I only had a relationship with Diana every month or every year, there wouldn't be a good marriage.

00:22:12.519 --> 00:22:16.240
A marriage is based on having a relationship every single day.

00:22:18.811 --> 00:22:19.006
We talk, we have communion.

00:22:19.006 --> 00:22:21.404
That's what I'm trying to tell you.

00:22:21.404 --> 00:22:23.320
That's the way it is with the Father.

00:22:23.320 --> 00:22:29.919
You must have a relationship with him and find things that will inspire you to keep going: books, tape series, whatever.

00:22:29.919 --> 00:22:34.1000
Back in the day, I used to buy a tape series every single time I got paid.

00:22:34.1000 --> 00:22:44.658
I'd find a tape series and I'd listen to that one tape series the whole time because we only got paid every two weeks.

00:22:44.658 --> 00:22:59.413
I said if I could listen to it every time, whether it would be usually Lester Sumrall or somebody like that, I'd find something and think, "Man, I want to listen to these old-timers.

00:22:59.413 --> 00:23:06.240
" I would listen to that whole tape series for two weeks and then I'd alternate them out just continually.

00:23:06.240 --> 00:23:09.279
Faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by the word of God.

00:23:12.160 --> 00:23:14.057
The only way you're going to get strong is with your faith growing.

00:23:14.057 --> 00:23:18.969
But faith works by love, so you've got to keep strife out.

00:23:18.969 --> 00:23:26.507
I'm telling you, it's like seeing an engine where the pistons and all the parts are moving in the engine so that you go really fast.

00:23:31.420 --> 00:23:34.120
But if one thing is off, that engine is not going to work right.

00:23:37.920 --> 00:23:38.640
That's the way it is in the spirit realm.

00:23:38.640 --> 00:23:51.177
You've got to make sure all those pistons are firing and all that stuff in the spirit is firing and going perfectly so that you're going forward in your spiritual walk.

00:23:51.177 --> 00:23:54.132
That's going to make that spiritual car go forward.

00:23:58.123 --> 00:24:02.660
If not, you're going to be idle and sitting by, asking, "Why am I still this way after all these years?

00:24:02.660 --> 00:24:04.559
How come nothing's changed?

00:24:04.559 --> 00:24:13.159
" Most people keep doing the same thing expecting different results, and that's the definition of insanity.

00:24:13.159 --> 00:24:23.279
That's why I say if it isn't working after 30 days, or if it isn't working after 60 days, we've got to make some changes in here.

00:24:27.840 --> 00:24:40.023
If what you're doing isn't getting you closer to God after a couple of weeks and you're saying, "Well, I'm still idly sitting by," the Bible says if we draw nigh to him, he'll draw nigh to us.

00:24:40.023 --> 00:24:42.613
So I'm just looking, "Father, I want more.

00:24:42.613 --> 00:24:44.320
