00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
You can help me pray until tomorrow.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Tomorrow's Tuesday and we'll pray again.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
We'll keep praying until the Lord says...

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
we are winners.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
We go through October 31st.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
We keep doing the things the Lord's called us to do.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.700
We've had 5,500 people praying right now, and I believe with all my heart there's power, for many hands make light work.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
We're on the victory side.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
We love you all.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
Remember, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
Jesus loves you so much and we love you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
God bless you and we'll see you again soon.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
